instructions = "The path to the flag is getting narrow! To navigate this obstacle course, you will need to combine multiple turns and movements in the correct order.

If the robot hits a wall or a piece of furniture, the program will fail. If you get stuck, try using the AI Assistant tab on the left for a hint, or slow down the execution speed using the Speed button to see exactly where your logic goes wrong."
intended_solution = "block: BeginBlock
  text: \"begin code\"
  children:
    - block: TurnBlock
      text: \"turn {}\"
      parameters:
        - \"right\"
    - block: MoveBlock
      text: \"move forward\"
    - block: MoveBlock
      text: \"move forward\"
    - block: TurnBlock
      text: \"turn {}\"
      parameters:
        - \"left\"
    - block: MoveBlock
      text: \"move forward\"
    - block: MoveBlock
      text: \"move forward\"
"

